9 AN ACT TO AMEND THE ARKANSAS BUSINESS CORPORATION ACT
10 OF 1987; TO AMEND THE UNIFORM LIMITED LIABILITY
11 COMPANY ACT; TO CLARIFY THE DEFINITION OF "PRINCIPAL
12 OFFICE" USED UNDER THE ARKANSAS BUSINESS CORPORATION
13 ACT OF 1987 AND THE UNIFORM LIMITED LIABILITY COMPANY
14 ACT; AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES.
